      </div>
      <h1 itemprop="headline">{pageTitle}</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Stoicism was the operating system of the Roman Empire's greatest leaders. Two thousand years later, it remains one of the most practically useful philosophies for anyone pursuing ambitious goals in an uncertain world.</p>
      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" style="display:none">
        <span itemprop="name">{author}</span>
      </span>
    </header>

    <figure class="article-hero">
